name: Amy and Ivor moccasins
description:
Re-order in the new year :)

AMY & IVOR is a small British business handcrafting traditional leather baby & toddler moccasins. 


Amy & Ivor baby and toddler moccasins are handmade to order. Made from Chrome free leather that is naturally soft, supple and breathable. The soft structure is kind to developing feet while also offering protection. They really do stay on tiny feet. Designed for indoor and light outdoor use.

Your moccasins will be beautifully packaged, a special treat for your little one or the perfect gift, 

PRICE:
£38 (this includes UK 1st class postage).
Payment is via PayPal.

Delivery costs to other countries will be quoted on an individual basis.

SIZE GUIDE: 
Find our Size Guide in 'Moccasin Sizing' photo. A helpful hint is to measure feet on a flat surface and ensure the child’s toes are pushed flat.

INSTRUCTIONS TO ORDER:
purchase via the 'purchase' button as normal with the colour wanted

Then email using the contact box to request size (see 'size guide' in photo album for measurements).


We will confirm your order once payment is received and then making begins. We endeavour to keep you updated of your orders progress. As a guideline it is our aim to turn orders around ready for dispatch in a two-week period, but this will be variable depending on the length of the order queue.

NOTE:
Our moccasins will take on a natural level of patina with wear and will soon start to mould to your child’s feet. After a while you will see an impression of your child’s foot on the leather sole - a sweet lasting memory of how tiny their feet once were!

These shoes are made from natural leather so irregularities and blemishes do occur - this is not a fault but a perfectly normal feature of leather. 

Our moccasins are designed for indoor and light outdoor use, however it is not advisable to let them get wet. If they do get wet allow them to dry naturally.

Be aware darker colours may bleed as dyed leather cannot be 100% colourfast.

Our shoes are handmade - every pair is unique!

RETURNS: 
We are happy to exchange for an alternative size if you find the size ordered does not fit. If this is the case you must notify us within 7 days of receipt of your moccasins & return them to us unworn & in their original packaging immediately after. The replacement pair will be made once your return is received.

name: Mini hand warmer
description:
Perfect for the cold days that are coming!

Mini hot water bottle hand warmer provides self-heating and rechargeable heat for your hands. 

The heat is activated by flexing a metal disc inside the gel. This produces warmth in seconds and will last for around 40 minutes.

You can reuse them by boiling it for 15 minutes until the contents have liquefied. It can then be reused.

How to use your hand warmer: Locate the small metal disc, bend the disc with your fingers until it clicks.  Wait a few seconds for the heat to spread through the hand warmer.  Squeeze and knead the gel to retain warmth for longer. keep inside the warmer pocket.

Material: synthetic/metal
Dimensions: Length: 9 cm, Width: 2 cm, Height: 13 cm
Diameter: cm
